  "comment": {
    "text": "The translation key \"PortalDeletion\" is used to display a message indicating that an artifact will be deleted. In the UI, it appears in a portal settings page as part of a deletion confirmation dialog. The phrase should refer to the specific product or application being deleted, using the product name provided by the user.",
